column4: <content>Tower of Babel, Rotterdam. The painting by Lucas van Valckenborch based on it (repr. Franz, fig. 254) and in Minkowski, rev.1963, p. 76; Munich (1642) is dated 1568, which in any case gives a terminius ante quem for the Rotterdam Tower of Babel.</content>
